  "title": "Event Activation Representative (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p>🎓 JUST GRADUATED? ORD DONE? NO EXPERIENCE? NO WORRIES!<br>\nJoin the frontlines of exciting events! 🚀</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What’s In It For You</strong><br>\n• 🎉 Live Campaign Activations – Bring events to life for top brands.<br>\n• 🤝 Client-Facing Experience – Build relationships face-to-face.<br>\n• 🕴 Sharpen Presentation Skills – Learn from experienced mentors.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why You’ll Love It Here:</strong><br>\n• ✨ Training provided, no background needed.<br>\n• 👯‍♀ Work with a fun, motivated team.<br>\n• 🎊 Active, engaging role – never boring.</p>\n<p>💸 Weekly Pay + Commission Bonuses!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Plus:</strong><br>\n• 📈 Level-up training and growth plans.<br>\n• 🧠 Opportunities to lead future activations.<br>\n• ✈ Travel perks for standout performers.</p>",
